WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
POV: the gripper approaches the cubes.

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:04.200
The blue cube moves into the center of view.

00:00:04.200 --> 00:00:06.200
The fingers close around the blue cube.

00:00:06.200 --> 00:00:08.800
The gripper lifts the blue cube cleanly.

00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:11.000
The arm carries the cube from the pickup area.

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:12.821
The cube is released, completing the correct pick.
